^b@2^*BMarty Bergen: ^*N|cp||at|After the 2@H bid, South should be content with a jump to 4@S. When the opponents open the bidding in 1st or 2nd seat slam is really unlikely. The only time you should even think about slam is when you have freakish distribution. 6-3-2-2 certainly does not qualify. Everyone passes.|mb|4SPPP|
